## Recursive Application

Φ²(LiquidDemocracy) = Φ(Φ(LiquidDemocracy))

The liquid democracy system can apply to itself:
- Delegation of delegation mechanisms
- Meta-governance of platform architecture
- Recursive revocability (revoking the right to revoke)
- Trust networks about trust networks

This creates the conditions for:
- Emergent constitutional moments
- Self-modifying governance protocols
